asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Flufman
description: Just your regular guy, by day, and to those that dont know me. Orphened at a young age during the wreck when my parents were lost in a tragic avoidable accident, I swore to always be on alert and save fluf from imminent peril.  With a vast inheritance of carrots and mentored in the fluffle by Black Velvet, Starlord, Hot Lips, Artemis and Hawkeye, some liken me to Gothams, Batman. I am discrete, well funded, have all the toys and tech you can imagine, humble yet charming and understated. Problems in your area? I will be there. Just raise the beacon of a carrot into the sky and I will be there in the fluf suit to help. Its very tightly fitted and the mask is especially powerful. In my downtime, I love to socialise and dance and help charities. When there is a special fluf in my life, Im sure you know what I am doing, my name says it all.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

Now this entertainer has kept fluf hopping on good wybes throughout the good and bad times. Legend has it that when escaping the wreck, Whitney was able to sooth predators into submission with her soft and gentle tones. Failing that, a focused ultra high frequency discharge can rupture any creatures brain. You do not want to be in front of her in that situation! Whitney has a huge range of hits such as Where Do Broken Flufs Go, Im your Fluf tonight, I Wanna Dance With Somefluffy, and her hit single from the movie Flufguard, I will always fluf you. If you ever get the opportunity to see her live, do not miss it.

description:
Sometimes love can make people do crazy things. Other times? It drives them completely insane. Such is the case with Miss Prowess Fluf, formerly Dr. Fluf. A promising psychologist and intern at Arkham Asylum in The Underground, Miss Prowess Fluf  was given the chance to get up close and personal with the Maker, an experience that wound up ending... badly. She became obsessed with her subject, and after falling madly in love with the Fluf Prince of Crime, she helped him escape the Underground.
In time, She came to realize the Prince was holding her back and she struck out on her own. She became an entrepreneur and a member of several slightly less-than-reputable super teams (including the Fluf Squad), Undergrounds all-girl gang the Fluf Sirens, and a traveling sideshow.

asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
